New Metadata Types in Digital Lending
Learn more about the new metadata types in Digital Lending.
Salesforce Flow
Create contract document
Use the new createClmContract value in the existing actionType field, which is on the FlowActionCall subtype of the Flow metadata type.
Check in contract document version
Use the new checkInContractDocumentVersion value in the existing actionType field, which is on the FlowActionCall subtype of the Flow metadata type.
Perform actions on a contract based on its status
Use the new performContractAction value in the existing actionType field, which is on the FlowActionCall subtype of the Flow metadata type.
Send contracts for e-signature
Use the new sendContractForESignature value in the existing actionType field, which is on the FlowActionCall subtype of the Flow metadata type.
